  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      539.98,
      315.72,
      553.02
    ],
    "text": "Section 354 of the Penal Code reads as follows,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      571.78,
      529.87,
      584.82
    ],
    "text": "\u201cWhoever kidnaps any person from Ceylon or from lawful guardianship shall be",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      591.58,
      529.88,
      604.62
    ],
    "text": "punished with imprisonment of either description for a term which may extend to",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      611.5,
      335.78,
      624.54
    ],
    "text": "seven years, and shall also be liable to fine\u201d",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      643.3,
      345.02,
      656.34
    ],
    "text": "Section 364 (2)(e) of the Penal Code reads as follows,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      675.13,
      188.33,
      688.17
    ],
    "text": "(2) \u201cWhoever\u2014",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      706.93,
      529.8,
      719.97
    ],
    "text": "(e) commits rape on a woman under eighteen years of age; shall be punished with",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      726.85,
      529.96,
      739.89
    ],
    "text": "rigorous imprisonment for a term not test than ten years and not exceeding twenty",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      746.65,
      529.79,
      759.69
    ],
    "text": "years and with fine and shall in addition be ordered to pay compensation of an",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      776.75,
      328.07,
      806.04
    ],
    "text": "Page 4 of 6",
    "fonts": [
      "Aptos",
      "Aptos,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      71.91,
      529.82,
      84.95
    ],
    "text": "amount determined by court to the person in respect of whom the offence was",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      91.73,
      364.43,
      104.77
    ],
    "text": "committed for the injuries caused to such person;",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      123.65,
      529.82,
      136.69
    ],
    "text": "Provided, however, that where the offence is committed in respect of a person",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      143.45,
      529.84,
      156.49
    ],
    "text": "under sixteen years of age, the court may, where the offender is a person under",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      163.25,
      529.95,
      176.29
    ],
    "text": "eighteen years of age and the intercourse has been with the consent of the person,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      183.05,
      440.57,
      196.09
    ],
    "text": "impose a sentence of imprisonment for term less than ten years.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      214.25,
      526.24,
      227.29
    ],
    "text": "Our Courts have consistently held that, when a Learned Trial Judge considers the",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      234.05,
      526.21,
      247.09
    ],
    "text": "mitigating and aggravating factors, there is a duty upon the Judge to give reasonable",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      253.85,
      526.49,
      266.89
    ],
    "text": "consideration to such factors. I am mindful that, in the present case, the starting point of",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      273.68,
      316.94,
      286.72
    ],
    "text": "the sentence for the offence of rape is ten years.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      305.6,
      530.07,
      318.64
    ],
    "text": "His Lordship S.N. Silva J (as he was then) in the case of Attorney General v. Ranasinghe",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      71.31,
      325.4,
      526.36,
      338.44
    ],
    "text": "and Others (1993) 2 SLR 81 had referred to the judgment of Kieth Billiam (1986) Volume",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      345.2,
      526.2,
      358.24
    ],
    "text": "Criminal Appeal Report 347, where the Court had identified the following instances as",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      365.12,
      184.29,
      378.16
    ],
    "text": "aggravating features.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      396.92,
      314.54,
      409.96
    ],
    "text": "\u201c1. Violence is used to commit the rape.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      428.72,
      329.46,
      441.76
    ],
    "text": "2. A weapon is used to frighten the victim.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      460.54,
      214.99,
      473.58
    ],
    "text": "3. Rape is repeated.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      492.46,
      502.5,
      505.5
    ],
    "text": "4. The Defendant had a previous conviction of rape or other serious offences.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      524.26,
      345.52,
      537.3
    ],
    "text": "5. The victim is either very old or very young.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      556.06,
      529.85,
      569.1
    ],
    "text": "Further held that \u201cwhere any one or more aggravating factors are present, the",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      575.98,
      529.74,
      589.02
    ],
    "text": "sentence should be substantially higher than the figure suggested as the starting",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      107.3,
      595.78,
      145.33,
      608.82
    ],
    "text": "point.\u201d",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      626.86,
      526.26,
      639.9
    ],
    "text": "In the present case, the starting point for sentencing in respect of the offence is ten years.",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      646.69,
      526.22,
      659.73
    ],
    "text": "Thereafter, it is incumbent upon the Learned Judge to exercise judicial discretion by",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      666.61,
      526.46,
      679.65
    ],
    "text": "weighing the aggravating and mitigating factors relevant to the circumstances. In this",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      686.41,
      526.49,
      699.45
    ],
    "text": "matter, the Learned High Court Judge has taken into consideration the following factors:",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      776.75,
      328.07,
      806.04
    ],
    "text": "Page 5 of 6",
    "fonts": [
      "Aptos",
      "Aptos,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      71.91,
      186.09,
      84.95
    ],
    "text": "Page 114 of the brief,",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      100.85,
      526.49,
      114.43
    ],
    "text": "\u201c\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca \u0db8\u0db8\u0db8 \u0db1\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0db8\u0db8\u0db8 \u0db1\u0da9\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dda \u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca\u0dd2\u0dad \u0dad\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dca\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0da0\u0dd4\u0dd2\u0dad \u0d85\u0dad\u0dbb \u0db4\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dba",
